----Usage
Enter a rule string in the designated input field.
Provide JSON data for evaluation in the second input field.
Click the "Create Rule" button to define your rule.
Click the "Evaluate Rule" button to see the evaluation result.
API Endpoints
POST /create_rule
Description: Creates a rule from the provided string.
Body: { "rule_string": "((age > 30 and department == 'Sales') or (age < 25 and department == 'Marketing'))" }
POST /evaluate_rule
Description: Evaluates the previously created rule against the provided JSON data.
Body: { "json_data": "{\"age\": 35, \"department\": \"Sales\", \"salary\": 60000, \"experience\": 6}" }
